'''James I. McCord''' (born 1919 in [[Breadalbane, Ontario]]; died February 19, 1990) was a president of [[Princeton Theological Seminary]]. He also won the 1986 [[Templeton Prize]].

==150 Years of Princeton Theological Seminary==
